description:

* Large, bright and welcoming front foyer with pendant lighting, large closet and extraordinary Fish Lake views.

* Secondary bedrooms offer so many options.  
* Full bath with wood floor.
* Laundry room with utility sink, cabinet storage and counter space.  Washer and dryer included.
Additional Features
* Quiet and private cul-de-sac street front.
* Paver driveway.
* Relaxing front porch.
* Newer roof (2017).

* Garage basement/storage

Enjoy big beautiful windows with inviting southern exposure and open concept floor plan. Designed with pristine finishes throughout including, granite counters, huge sit down kitchen island, solid wood floors, tiled laundry and baths floors, great room with electric linear fireplace and lower rec room with gas fireplaces, enamel cabinets, doors, case and base on main and upper floors with stained lower level finishes.   Entertaining is easy with the wet bar and large recreational room. Have a private workout in the exercise room or relax out on the deck. For sale: $654,190. Take a Virtual Tour of the Prescott floorplan! Welcome to Lennar's Prescott floorplan! This spacious home offers 3,380 square feet to 4,599 square feet of living space and is the largest in our Traditional Collection. The Prescott foyer opens to a flex room in the front of the home and a powder room. An oversized island in the kitchen overlooks the dinette that leads into the family room. Located off of the garage entrance is a mudroom with a private study tucked behind it. The upper level of the Prescott offers three bedrooms plus an owner's suite. The owner's suite has a large, luxurious private bathroom as well as a spacious walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms all have access to either a private or jack and jill bathroom. The upper level also features a great multi-purpose bonus room and laundry room.

For sale: $484,500. Mint condition 2 story home with recently updated carpet, paint, appliances, granite countertops, and light fixtures. This home features main level den with fireplace & french doors, office with built-ins, formal dining room, giant foyer with vaulted ceilings, living room with fireplace, large kitchen with walkout to deck and views of the private wooded back yard. Upper level features a master suite, with large walk-in closet, master bath with soaking tub, dual vanities, and separate shower. Upper-level laundry, and 3 additional bedrooms with 6-panel doors, and window treatments throughout. description: Recently sold: $214,900. Beautifully updated  home, Model condition. New: kitchen SS appliances, double sink, faucet, ceramic back splash wall, hardwood style floors, carpet, vinyl, freshly painted, vanity top in upper bath, water heater, C/A, water softener. Main level has 9 foot ceiling, 42" cabinets, center island & breakfast bar, beautiful built-in entertainment  center with gas fireplace. Upper level has 2 bedrooms, MBR has a large walk-in closet, loft, large laundry/utility area, great fenced front porch. 10+!

Recently sold: $499,900. Gorgeous home checks all the boxes....maintenance free ease, single level living convenience, and a fabulous 55+ community loaded with extraordinary amenities sure to fulfill your every wish!  Plus, Rush Creek Golf Course is just across the street and the backyard overlooks Maple Creek Park!
Built in 2016, this stunning home showcases premium finishes, an open & light filled design + nearly every upgrade allowed! Outstanding wood floors flow throughout the main level with its tall knockdown ceilings, multiple oversized windows + upper transoms, and beautiful millwork & built-ins. Impressive gathering areas include a well appointed kitchen featuring granite counters, stainless appliances, rich cherry cabinetry and an adjoining dining area.  These spaces flow effortlessly to the inviting living room highlighted by a focal gas fireplace with stone surround and flanking built-ins, walk-out access to the backyard deck + large, south facing windows flood the area with natural light all year round!
Owner's suite is a relaxing oasis boasting a large sleeping area with an adjoining sunny sitting room, walk-in closet, and private bath with dual sinks/vanities, private water closet & tile shower with dual shower heads & built-in seating.
The main level also offers a 2nd bedroom, full bath, den/office (off the foyer), and laundry for your convenience.  Bonus: over 2,000 square feet of unfinished space awaits within the lower level....great open storage or finish the space for instant equity.
Premier Community & Shared Amenities:  13,500 sq. ft. Clubhouse: ballroom, crafts, learning center, billiards, exercise room, dance/aerobic studio.  Outdoor pool, spa & patio + indoor pool, spa & sauna.  Walking trails, gazebo + nearby parks & golf.  Tennis, pickleball, bocce ball + putting green.  Community social calendar filled with events/activities.

description:
Recently sold: $310,000. Contact the official listing agent, Julie Betzler with Realty Group, Inc. for the most accurate and up to date info on this awesome property! Fantastic split-entry home with partial finished lookout lower level, and partial unfinished with 2 egress windows for the possibility of two future additional bedrooms! Property is on .35 acres, fenced backyard, mature trees, lush lawn in a developed neighborhood. Home is finished with approximately 1,938 square feet and situated on a lookout lot with level backyard that includes a 12? x 10? freshly painted back deck with steps down to the yard. Property is within close proximity to parks, trails, Weaver Lake, public launch, a hospital, restaurants, golf course, major highways, conveniences and in the Osseo school district and award-winning Rush Creek Elementary school boundaries!  Call it home today!!

This one owner home was built in 1992, has a charming covered front concrete porch, great curb appeal with landscaping, trees, manicured yard, gutters and front storm door, 2 car attached garage with epoxied floors, newer driveway apron.  Windows in the upper level were newly installed in 2017.

The upper main level features a welcoming living room with front yard facing windows, neutral (just shampooed) carpet, vaulted ceiling, wood rails, ceiling fan and opens to the informal dining room with glass doors that leads out to the backyard deck.  The kitchen has been recently updated with stainless appliances, including a gas range, marble tile backsplash, Silestone counters and oil rubbed bronze fixtures and hardware and under  cabinet task lighting.  The floors are laminate, cabinets Oak and check out the beautiful glass front cabinet doors for display.

The upper main level also features three bedrooms on one level, which is hard to find in a split entry home (large upper level footprint). The master bedroom has double closets and a private master ¾ bathroom with in-floor heat in the tile floors.  There is also another full bathroom on the upper main level.

The lookout lower level is partially finished with a huge L-shaped family room that looks out to the back yard and front yard, plus a wood burning fireplace (please note owners have not used this fireplace in many years).  There is an additional ¾ bathroom in the lower level and under-stair storage. There is also a large unfinished area that houses the laundry and mechanicals, plus area for storage, hobbies, exercise, workshop OR finished this area to your liking, includes 2 additional egress windows, so possibility of adding 2 more bedrooms in the lower level.  You decide and call it home today!

description:
Recently sold: $365,000. Upper Level
* Spacious living room perfect for entertaining, closet for all your extras and wall-of-windows brings the serene outdoor views in! 
* Kitchen offers solid hardwood floor, abundant cabinetry, granite countertops, stunning new champagne finish faucet and Koehler sink, new refrigerator and dishwasher, breakfast bar, above the sink window box, workstation with under cabinet lighting and recessed lighting.
* Sun-splashed dining room offers ceiling fan with pendant light along with plentiful natural light and backyard views.  Easy deck access.
* Master bedroom with wood floor, walk-in closet, ceiling fan and peaceful views.  Private 3/4 Master bath with new tile floor, tiled shower and window.
* 2 bedrooms on one level both with so much space!
* Full bath offers tile flooring, tiled shower/bath area and new elegant marble vanity. Quality craftsmanship throughout.
Lower Level
* Family room highlights stone accent wall plus wood burning fireplace and built-ins, perfect for relaxation.
* Huge recreation room with wet bar offering tiered bar area and tiled bar top, beverage refrigerator, sink and cabinet storage.  Walkout to backyard.
* Large secondary bedroom with walk-in closet?so many options.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor and tile surround in shower with 2 shower heads and granite vanity.
* Mechanical room hosts laundry room and can dual as craft or hobby area with so much space, cabinetry and natural light. 
Additional Features
* Lower heated garage with backyard door access, epoxy floors, cabinets with counter space. Great workshop!
* Main level garage with windows, service door and extra space for storage. Plus, brand new garage doors with windows for natural light.
* Dual decks and expansive backyard.
* Additional hook-ups on upper level for second laundry room! Currently large storage closet or pantry. 
* Whole house HEPPA filtration and UV air sanitizer.  
* Convenient grill gas line to deck. 
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

Also located on the main floor is the separate Dining Room with buffet, 2nd bedroom, Laundry/Mud Room, and half bath. Exquisite main floor Master Suite has a private bath with ceramic tile, double vanity, separate tiled walk-in shower, relaxing soaker tub, and walk-in closet. The walkout lower level has a Family Room with fireplace and wet bar, Exercise Room, 2 bedrooms, and full bath.

description:
Recently sold: $465,000. One of the finest homes in Maple Grove is phenomenal and offered for sale! Don't let this one slip by!
Cherry woodwork throughout the walkout family room accents the stunning stone fireplace that keeps this room warm and cozy. Belly up to the full bar topped in granite while enjoying the heated tile floor. Display your prized possessions in the lighted curio cabinet down the wide hallway or in the built-in entertainment center.  
A dual-purpose main floor room can be used as a home office or a formal dining space complete with French doors and a bay window. 
Whip up a tasty meal at the granite center island in the kitchen with stainless steel appliances, plenty of custom cabinetry, and a patio door that leads to the deck for additional outdoor entertaining.
4 of the big bedrooms are all on the same level and the Master Sanctuary has a tray vault, huge closet, and its own private bath. Luxurious to say the least with granite vanity, tile flooring, jetted tub, and separate glass shower. Double sinks are installed in one of the remaining full baths for convenience.
With an open concept floor plan, the living space has a gorgeous gas fireplace surrounded in natural stone and custom-built corner cabinets. 
Stow items away neatly in the overhead storage space in the insulated 3 stall garage. The home has 2 additional storage rooms keeping it nice and tidy.
A sprinkler system allows for lush landscaping so that the wooded trails can be thoroughly enjoyed.
All of this and so much more will delight your eyes and senses! See it today!
Chris Fritch Team Keller Williams Classic Realty

description:
Recently sold: $453,000. Executive Custom Built End Unit Townhouse! Meticulously Maintained and the quality of this home is impeccable! Rare 3 Car Garage, Open floor plan, high tray & vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, gorgeous hardwood floors, Alder cabinetry and Maple millwork, chef's kitchen with large center island/ breakfast bar, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas fireplace with tile surround, sunroom that walks out to a maintenance free deck, master suite with a huge walk-in closet, hydro-massage tub, double sinks, separate shower, and tiled floors, main level laundry/ mudroom, light and bright lower level has a spacious family room, wet bar, 2nd gas fireplace with built-ins, recessed lighting, a ¾ tiled bath, 2 large comfy bedrooms both with walk-in closets, carpet, and ceiling fans, large storage area (21x21), lots of green space and more! 

Come Check Out This One Level Living in Brockton Woods!

Recently sold: $180,000. Mint 5 bd home offers true one level living! Light, bright and open floor plan. Quiet street of higher priced exec homes. Near parks and trails of Fish Lake and Weaver Lake. Close to Shoppes of Arbor Lakes, schools and freeways. Quick close possible. Must see!

Recently sold: $449,991. Take a Virtual Tour of the Lewis EI floorplan! Welcome to Lennar's Lewis EI floorplan. The stunning Lewis EI ranges from 2,692 to 3,556 square feet and provides homeowners with an open concept layout - perfect for hosting and entertaining family and friends. The main level of the Lewis EI offers a spacious kitchen that overlooks the great room. The kitchen is equipped with an island, walk-in pantry, plenty of counter space, and a dinette. A flex room, powder room, and a mudroom off of the garage entrance completes the main level of the Lewis EI. The upper level of the Lewis EI has a versatile loft area and four bedrooms - including the owner's suite. The large owner's suite includes a beautiful bathroom and spacious walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms on the upper level all also include walk-in closets. A full bathroom and a conveniently located laundry room complete the upper level.

description:
Recently sold: $357,000. Main Level
* Welcoming open foyer with closet and garage entry.
* Kitchen features ample cabinetry, granite countertops, center island with tiered bar, cook top, wall oven, stem rack, above sink window, recessed plus under cabinet and pendent lighting.
* Formal dining room offers pendant lighting and convenient serving area between kitchen and dining room.  Easy deck access.
Upper Level
* Living room features floor-to-ceiling stone gas fireplace with wood mantel, vaulted ceiling and easy screen porch access. 
* Office with French doors and tranquil views.
* Spacious master bedroom with 2 large walk-in closets and private deck access.  Vanity area includes sink with private water closet and custom marble/granite updated shower.
* Attractive full bath.
Lower Level
* Family room highlights floor-to-ceiling brick wood burning fireplace with wood mantel, built-in shelving, heated tile floor and patio access.
* Adjacent wet bar with granite countertop and matching backsplash with decorative tile finish, vessel sink, full refrigerator, pendant and recessed lights.
* 2 bedrooms on one level.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor, tiled walk-in shower stall and beautiful granite vanity. 
Basement
* Finish for nearly 2900 sq ft.
Additional
* Screen porch with ceiling fan and deck access.
* All new carpet.
* Walk out to large concrete patio.
* New drain tile, sump pump, and hot water heater.
* Upper level wrap around deck.
* Expansive fully fenced flat backyard.
  All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

* New carpet.

description:
Recently sold: $527,500. Main Level
* Gorgeous 2-story entry with foyer piano windows and cascading staircase is a warm welcome to any guest.
* Gleaming hardwood floors flow from foyer to kitchen and dinette.
* Living room with decorative piano windows, vaulted ceiling and grand front wall windows offers abundant natural light.  
* Formal dining room with lit niche and serene mealtime views.
* Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, wall oven, gas cooktop, tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, granite countertops, center island with sink, walk-in pantry and recessed lighting.  
* Window wrapped dinette with built-in hutch and easy patio access offering year-round picturesque views.
* Family room highlights floor-to-ceiling stone gas burning fireplace, custom built-ins, piano windows plus wall-of -windows offering tranquil backyard views.  Open floor plan.
* Conveniently located office just off foyer with French doors and front yard views.
* Laundry room with boot bench including cubbies, coat hooks and storage drawers, window, utility sink, shelving, ample cabinetry and counter space. Washer and dryer included.
* Mud room offers double door closet and garage foyer.
* Attractive 1/2 bath with tile flooring and pedestal sink.
Upper Level
* Master suite with double door entry, vaulted ceiling with fan and peaceful views.  Luxurious master bath features tile flooring, double sink vanity, window, linen closet, private water closet with window, walk-in closet, soaking tub and shower.
* 5 bedrooms on one level. All bedrooms with walk-in closets.
* Loft with balcony overlook and hallway linen closet.
* Spacious full bath with tile flooring, double sink vanity, window, private water closet and shower/bath area.
Lower Level
* Amusement room features gas fireplace, recessed ceiling with accent lighting, sconce lights, decorative recessed wall niche and projector ceiling holder.  
* Wet bar with tiered granite bar area, tiled counter space, beverage refrigerator, wine rack, tile floor, pendant and recessed lights.
* Recreation room perfect for billiards, darts, so much more?
* Media room with tiered seating, sconce lighting, storage closet, projector and screen.
* Secondary bedroom offers French doors.  Could also be used as an exercise room.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor, granite vanity with vessel sink and impressive walk-in tiled shower.
Additional Features
* Patio and expansive backyard.
* 2015 New roof.

description:
Recently sold: $530,000. Main Level
* 2-story foyer with wood floor, dual closets, chandelier, cascading staircase and grand transom window light is an impressive welcome to any guest.
* Living room with vaulted ceiling, built-ins and front yard views.
* Family room highlights floor-to-ceiling brick gas fireplace flanked by windows plus wall-of-windows offering panoramic pond views.  Custom built-ins to keep you organized or display your favorite collections. 
* Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, wall oven, gas cooktop, breakfast bar with seating, granite countertops, extensive cabinetry, tile backsplash, recessed and under cabinet lights.
* Adjacent window wrapped dinette offers open floor plan for entertaining. Easy deck access.
* Formal dining room with elegant recessed ceiling and serene mealtime views.
* Office or bedroom with built-in desk station?so many options.
* Conveniently located laundry room with cabinetry, counter space, sink and window.
* Attractive full bath with tile floor, pedestal sink and tile shower/bath area.
Upper Level
* Master suite offers double door entry, tray ceiling, walk-in closet and peaceful views.  Luxurious master bath with tile floor, double sink vanity, window, tile surround whirlpool tub and tiled shower.
* 3 Spacious bedrooms on one level. 
* Full Jack & Jill bath with tile floor, tile bath/shower, and room adjacent sink vanity areas.
Lower Level
* Expansive amusement room features floor-to-ceiling brick gas fireplace flanked by windows, perfect for relaxing with a good movie, billiards, foosball, ping-pong, and so much more? 
* Recreation room with bar area offering tons of cabinet storage, counterspace, adjacent built-in shelving and multi desk workstations?so much to offer.  Easy deck access.  
* Den with closet.  Great exercise room, craft room, toy room++.
* Spacious 3/4 bath with tile floor and shower.
* Storage room perfect for all your extras.
Additional Features
* 3 car garage with loads of storage, newer concrete driveway, stamped concreted edging and decorative walk-way. Wifi garage door openers and new garage doors.
* Upgraded James Hardie Board siding. 
* Zone HVAC with Wifi thermostat and humidifier.
* Stunning outdoor accent up-lighting.
* Many newer windows.
* 2015 water softener.  75 gallon hot water heater.
* Clothes chute.
* Cul-de-sac street front.
* Main level and lower level deck, paver patio, basketball court.
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

description:
Recently sold: $620,000. Main Level
* Gorgeous 2-story entry with foyer transom window, coat closet and dual cascading staircase is a warm welcome to any guest.
* Gleaming Brazilian hardwood floors flow from foyer to kitchen, dinette and bath.
* Office with elegant French doors and front yard view.
* Living room with vaulted ceiling, grand windows plus piano windows offers abundant natural light.  
* Formal dining room with pillared archway entrance and serene mealtime views.
* Kitchen features stainless steel appliances including gas cooktop, double convection wall ovens, new refrigerator, tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, granite countertops, center island with sink and seating, walk-in pantry, recessed and under cabinet lighting.  
* Window wrapped dinette with adjacent workstation and easy deck access offering year-round picturesque views. 
* Impressive 2-story family room highlights floor-to-ceiling stone gas fireplace flanked by windows and built-ins.  Wall-of -windows offering tranquil views.  Open floor plan.  
* Convenient main floor laundry with tile floor, window, utility sink, drying rack, ample cabinetry and counter space.
* Mud room offers tile floor, walk-in closet, boot bench, storage cubbies with coat hooks and garage foyer.
* Attractive 1/2 bath with wood flooring and pedestal sink.
Upper Level
* Master suite with double door entry, vaulted ceiling with fan and peaceful views.  Luxurious master bath features tile flooring, dual deluxe vanities, private water closet, walk-in closet, windows, Kohler jet tub and large shower with dual shower heads.
* 4 spacious bedrooms on one level.
* Large full bath with tile flooring, double sink vanity, private water closet with shower/bath.
Lower Level
* Amusement room features floor-to-ceiling stone gas fireplace flanked by built-ins, stone and solid wood pillar entrance, pendant lighting, recessed lights and wall-of-windows.
* Recreation room with built-in cabinets, adjacent wet bar includes concrete bar top, sink, tile backsplash, wine rack, SubZero 96 bottle wine chiller with 2 refrigerated drawers.  Walk-out to patio.
* Studio/Hobby room/Office offers custom built-ins with concrete countertops and modern glass shelving, waterfall art, wood floor, in-floor heat and storage closet.
* Den with French doors is perfect for relaxing with a great movie, book or gaming.
* Exercise room offers rubber mat flooring and mirrored closet doors.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor and countertop with vessel sink, tiled shower with sitting area and impressive steaming capabilities.
Additional Features
* Main level Brazilian Ipe deck.
* Heated garage.
* Built-in Bose speakers.
* 2019 - Bryant High Efficient Furnace and 2017 - 50 gallon hot water heater. 
* Large storage rooms and closets!
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

* 2-story entry with foyer transom window, chandelier and cascading staircase is a warm welcome to any guest.
* Hardwood floors flow from foyer to family room, office, kitchen, dinette and bath.
* Office with elegant French doors, wall-of built-ins, crown molding and front yard view.
* Formal living room with abundant natural light.  
* Formal dining room offers crown molding, double track ceiling and serene mealtime views.
* Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, granite countertops, above the sink window, center island with wine refrigerator, workstation, recessed and pendant lighting.  
* Dinette with easy deck access offering year-round picturesque views. Adjacent butler/coffee bar with sink, granite countertop, and under cabinet lighting.
* Impressive 2-story family room highlights tile surround gas fireplace with wood mantel flanked by windows and ceiling fan.   
* Convenient main floor laundry with tile floor, window, utility sink, ample cabinetry and counter space.
* Mud room offers tile floor, closet and garage foyer.
* Attractive 1/2 bath with wood flooring and pedestal sink.
Upper Level
* Master suite with double door entry, detailed millwork, tray ceiling with fan and peaceful views.  Luxurious master bath features heated tile flooring, dual deluxe granite vanities with sitting vanity area, private water closet with tile shower, walk-in closet, windows, tile surround soaking tub and linen closet.
* 4 spacious bedrooms on one level.
* Large full bath with tile flooring, granite vanity, private water closet with shower/bath.
Lower Level
* Recreation room offers recessed lighting and double door closets for all your extras.  Perfect for relaxing, entertaining, gaming and more! 
* Secondary bedroom with so many options.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor and linen closet.
* Storage rooms or finish as desired.
Additional Features
* Main level deck with steps to expansive backyard.
* Front concrete stamped patio.
* Large clean storage.
* 2018 New Furnace & A/C.
* Newer windows throughout.
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.

Recently sold: $240,000. Gorgeous Townhome! Shows like new construction! New paint new carpet throughout! High kitchen cabinets, 9' main ceilings, 3 bedrooms on one level, oversized bedroom windows, walk-out patio w/ huge backyard. Super location, close to HWY 94 and shopping!

description: Recently sold: $324,900. Great outdoor space & tastefully updated interior on fenced corner lot! New flooring thru-out:  Carpet upstairs & down, vinyl plank on main. All new white trim on main, fresh grey paint, kitchen cabinets refreshed w/white paint. Main level laundry & 1/2 bath. Lots of daylight! 3 beds on upper level w/full bathroom. Lower level makes great flex space! Backyard deck w/ pergola. Convenient location w/easy access to 494, 94, & all Maple Grove has to offer! See highlight sheet for full list of details.

Recently sold: $345,000. Turn key opportunity to own in the Copper Marsh neighborhood and within blocks of the highly desirable Rush Creek Elementary. This beautifully updated home has the features you've been waiting for including a spacious floor plan with vaulted ceilings, deck overlooking a private, fenced back yard with amazing wetland views, a beautifully updated master bath, gas fireplace, main floor laundry, newer roof and interior paint. Kitchen features granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and wood floors. The unfinished lower level allows you to finish as you desire. Just a short walk to Hidden Meadows Park and trail system.

description: Recently sold: $424,900. Resort-at-home living at The Four Seasons at Rush Creek 55+ community. Main floor bdrm & laundry.Beautiful open flr plan w/ beautiful wood grain laminate flooring.Terrific home for entertaining friends & family.Gourmet kitchen w/granite ctrs & dbl oven.Lrg family rm w/marble surround gas FP.Lots of natural light.10 year Structural warranty.Fantastic amenities no community can match:13, 500 square-foot clubhouse provides amenities any active adult would want/need.Residents have access to their own learning center, craft hall, ballroom, catering kitchen, billiards & card room.There is an exercise room, aerobics/dance studio & indoor pool.After a hard workout active adults can relax in the saunas or indoor whirlpool spa.Those w/a competitive spirit will love the tennis court, pickleball courts, bocce ball courts & putting green. Looking to relax-appreciate the sparkling outdoor spa, pool & patio.No matter what your hobbies are, you ll be sure to find an amenity that sparks your interest.
